  "texts": [
    "Since online communities will continue to grow, computational technologies that make sense of big data and deep learning divisive consumer sentiments are needed (Kumar et al., 2020; Mikalef & Krogstie, 2020).",
    "Insightful consumer data can be gleaned from user-generated material on social networking sites, allowing for more informed business decisions.",
    "An optimization framework for studying commercials on the object level was created by Zhang et al. (2020).",
    "Some of how artificial intelligence has applied to the media include consumer content suggestions, consumer connection, the enhanced mood of the audience, content optimization, content management, content production, consumer insights, and functional robotics (Chan-Olmsted, 2019).",
    "Marketers anticipate that AI-based apps, such as virtual assistants and programmatic advertising, will soon constitute the backbone of digital marketing (De Bruyn et al., 2020)."
